---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Waterfalls | Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
description: "Fine art landscape photography collection exploring waterfalls, movement, stillness and the passage of time."
---

<section class="collection-hero">
  <img src="/assets/images/waterfalls.jpg" alt="Waterfalls">

  <div class="collection-hero-content">
    <p class="subtitle">Collection 02</p>
    <h1>Waterfalls</h1>
    <p>Where movement meets stillness.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="fine-art-story">

  <div class="story-text">
    <p>
      Water is never still. It moves, carves, disappears and returns, carrying light through the landscape.
    </p>
  </div>

  {% for photo in waterfalls %}
    <figure class="story-image {{ photo.class }} reveal">
      <img 
  src="{{ photo.src }}" 
  alt="{{ photo.alt }}"
     loading="lazy"
   decoding="async"
  class="lightbox-image"
  data-full="{{ photo.src }}"
  data-title=""
    >
    </figure>
  {% endfor %}

</section>